The workspace contains a mix of legacy and active development projects, each with its own `.env` configuration file. These files are scattered across directories like `/backend/api`, `/frontend/admin-panel`, `/microservices/auth-service`, and `/legacy/inventory-system`. For the security audit scheduled for Q3 2024, we must identify and catalog all exposed credentials to assess potential risk.

