The script must handle various formats, including lines with export prefixes (`export DB_PASS=...`), inline comments, and multi-line values. It should ignore empty lines and variables without clear sensitive markers. The final CSV output, `security_audit_credentials_2024-07-10.csv`, will be encrypted and shared exclusively with the security team for analysis and remediation planning.